        <p class="bold">Grid View Test Cases:&#160;</p>
        <ul class="checkbox">
            <li>All columns are sortable (A-Z and Z-A) (if applicable).</li>
            <li>Columns are resizable and this setting will be retained when closed and reopened (if applicable).</li>
